"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:50:33.000Z","msg":"美國全部亞洲盟友都被美國閹晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果中國當時跟唔到蘇聯佬，下場都會差唔多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:00:51.000Z","msg":"就係跟左蘇聯先變到而家咁撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0bb85ce389b0f1e5538b448a83435ce0370ac8","tid":520371,"uid":123711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:10:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"795275ad0e1b070c3652466cb9cf50e8a92757f8","tid":520371,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣交足保護費比美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蔡英文急急通知美國<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/05/realtime/4396343.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2Frealtime%2F4396343.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=906a8e50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n針對中國大陸民用航空局啟用M503航線北上運行及相關銜接航線，美國國務院表示，美國反對任何一方片面採取行動改變兩岸現狀。<br />\n<br />\n未具名的國務院官員4日透過電子郵件回覆本報記者指出，美方關切北京未經與台灣當局協商，修改在台灣海峽使用的民航航線。<br />\n<br />\n「我們反對任何一方片面採取行動改變兩岸現狀。」國務院官員表示，美方鼓勵北京與台北當局在尊嚴與尊重的基礎上，進行建設性對話；兩岸民航與安全相關問題，應該經由雙方對話決定。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸民用航空局網站4日發布，當天開始啟用M503南向北航線及相關銜接航線，並稱該航線為民航航線，大陸空管部門與台灣方面會保持技術性溝通。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會主委張小月隨後舉行記者會表達嚴正抗議，表示陸方未在兩岸協商溝通的情形下，逕自啟用M503南向北航路及W121、122、123航路，陸方此舉是「刻意以民航包裝對台灣的不當企圖」；我方已要求對岸立即停止相關飛航行動，如陸方一意孤行，將必須承擔任何影響兩岸關係的嚴重後果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/2912857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F2912857&d=lWL7howqbzzOWngGq1lCxnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d1a1a626\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/2912857</a>"},{"pid":"2844f0625fd34856a033d6e2d4c443c31c05a9c7","tid":520371,"uid":56432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"一早時間表<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/230423_46ee7e31280be59753d6bca4ee5b1097.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F230423_46ee7e31280be59753d6bca4ee5b1097.jpg&h=31d49e5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"099f243ce03a5be148a318dbee187d29fc197a4d","tid":520371,"uid":139993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:56:06.000Z","msg":"到時共匪打輸比台灣就係共產黨滅亡的徵兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023084b3cfe9ca014c57a62781672d6986bc19a8","tid":520371,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T16:28:32.000Z","msg":"ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩棲攻擊力近零<br />\n<br />\n武統佢老母咩"},{"pid":"75dd00d7403ee430a42cf5ccc119d664ee67b08a","tid":520371,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T16:38:14.000Z","msg":"下，打台灣？<br />\n用口打阿？"},{"pid":"3d08f887e9ca24a38a7609eea61daf432443ea30","tid":520371,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2844f0625fd34856a033d6e2d4c443c31c05a9c7","tid":520371,"uid":56432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"一早時間表<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/230423_46ee7e31280be59753d6bca4ee5b1097.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F230423_46ee7e31280be59753d6bc